WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:04.033 --> 00:00:08.567
&gt;&gt; With the comments gadget,
visitors can post a comment,

00:00:08.567 --> 00:00:10.968
reply to a comment,

00:00:10.968 --> 00:00:12.701
or add a video.

00:00:12.701 --> 00:00:16.834
They can also translate posts
into their preferred language.

00:00:16.834 --> 00:00:20.801
As a site owner, you can delete
any inappropriate posts.

00:00:20.801 --> 00:00:22.167
To get the comments gadget,

00:00:22.167 --> 00:00:24.868
go to google.com/friendconnect.

00:00:24.868 --> 00:00:28.601
Click on social gadgets,

00:00:28.601 --> 00:00:31.267
then "Comments."

00:00:31.267 --> 00:00:34.567
Set your options,

00:00:34.567 --> 00:00:37.501
choose your gadget size,

00:00:37.501 --> 00:00:43.100
then choose the colors you want
for your gadget.

00:00:43.100 --> 00:00:44.501
Click generate code

00:00:44.501 --> 00:00:49.133
and copy the snippet
into the body of your HTML.

00:00:49.133 --> 00:00:52.567
Go to google.com/friendconnect
to get started.

